"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rt\"><code>&lt;rt&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rtc\"><code>&lt;rtc&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>S\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sumário","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <em>Elemento </em><em>HTML </em><em>de Navegação</em> (<code>&lt;nav&gt;</code>) representa uma seção de uma página que aponta para outras páginas ou para outras áreas da página, ou seja, uma seção com links de navegação.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><em>Notas de utilização:</em></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Nem todos os links de um documento devem estar dentro de um elemento <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code>, o qual é destinado apenas para grupos importantes de links de navegação; tipicamente o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a> contém uma lista de links que não precisam estar em um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n <li>Um documento pode ter vários elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, por exemplo, um para navegação no site e outro para navegação dentro da página.</li>\n <li>Agentes de usuário, como leitores de tela para usuários deficientes, podem utilizar este elemento para determinar se a renderização inicial do conteúdo do mesmo deve ser omitida.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"Contexto de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Conteúdo permitido</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"en/HTML/Content categories#flow content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Omissão de tag</td>\n   <td>Nenhuma, tanto a tag de início quanto a de fim são obrigatórias</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Elementos-pai permitidos</td>\n   <td>Quaisquer elementos que permitam conteúdo de fluxo. Note que um elemento <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> não deve descender de um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Documento normativo</td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/sections.html#the-nav-element\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">HTML5, seção 4.4.3</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento não possui outros atributos além dos <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Global_attributes\" rel=\"internal\">atributos globais</a>, comuns a todos os elementos.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interface_dom","title":"Interface DOM","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento implementa a interface <code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/element\" title=\"en/DOM/element\">HTMLElement</a></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Página inicial<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Sobre<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Contato<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibilidade","title":"Compatibilidade","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.10</td>\n   <td>4.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>2.2</td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.0</td>\n   <td>5.0 (iOS 4.2)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Outros elementos relacionados à seções: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Seções_e_estrutura_HTML5\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Seções e esboços de um documento HTML5</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect4\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect5\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"sumário"},{"text":"Contexto de uso","id":"contexto_de_uso"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Interface DOM","id":"interface_dom"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Compatibilidade","id":"compatibilidade"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O Elemento HTML de Navegação (<nav>) representa uma seção de uma página que aponta para outras páginas ou para outras áreas da página, ou seja, uma seção com links de navegação.","popularity":0.0022,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"nav","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<nav>: The Navigation Section element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<nav>: El elemento de sección de navegación","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<nav> : l'élément de section de navigation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<nav>: ナビゲーションセクション要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<nav>: 탐색 구획 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Элемент секции навигации <nav>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<nav>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<nav>","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/nav","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/nav/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav","title":"nav"}],"pageTitle":"nav - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}